---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Evan Today - your guide to personal finance and fintech in Indonesia.">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Evan Today</h1>
		<div class="prose">
			<p>
				Welcome to Evan Today — your trusted source for personal finance insights, fintech reviews,
				and money management tips tailored for Indonesia and Southeast Asia.
			</p>
			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				We believe that financial literacy is the foundation of financial freedom. Our mission is to
				make personal finance accessible, practical, and actionable for everyone in Southeast Asia.
				Whether you're just starting your financial journey or looking to optimize your wealth-building
				strategy, we're here to help.
			</p>
			<h2>What We Cover</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Personal Finance</strong> — Budgeting, saving, and building emergency funds</li>
				<li><strong>Fintech</strong> — Reviews and comparisons of digital wallets, payment apps, and financial tools</li>
				<li><strong>Investing</strong> — Stock market basics, mutual funds, and wealth building strategies</li>
				<li><strong>Cryptocurrency</strong> — Understanding crypto, blockchain, and digital assets</li>
				<li><strong>Insurance</strong> — Finding the right coverage for your needs</li>
				<li><strong>Digital Banking</strong> — The best digital banks and their features</li>
			</ul>
			<h2>Why Trust Us</h2>
			<p>
				Every article we publish is thoroughly researched and written with accuracy in mind. We focus on
				providing practical, unbiased information that you can actually use to improve your financial life.
			</p>
			<p>
				Have a question or suggestion? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> — we'd love to hear from you.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
